text:
Trump-triggered and unglued Rosie O’Donnell predicts how GOP’s ‘coup d’état’ will end Posted at 5:48 pm on February 22, 2017 by Doug P. Share on Facebook Share on Twitter 
Donald Trump has so triggered the Hollywood Left that Rosie O’Donnell’s tweets are looking a lot like Cher’s. O’Donnell agrees that the Republicans took control in some sort of “coup” but also predicted how it’ll all end: @Rosie True, his coup d'état worked. R's have all 3 branches, kept judges vacant to fill, gerrymandered seats. Voting will take yrs to fix. 
— Joy M (@Joie_de_Vivre__) February 22, 2017 YES BUT WE ALL SEE WHAT HE HAS DONE – AND THEY WILL ALL COME TUMBLING DOWN IN AN ORANGE MUDSLIDE OF TREASON AND GUILTY #CRIMINALtrump #USA https://t.co/FMpi7M2txz
